snippet.title: Jesus Caught On Cam After A Church Bell Tower in Phillippines Collapsed

localized.description:
https://youtu.be/dhg1DziSeZc ◀Click this link for a much clearer video of christ

One of the worst disasters that hit the Phillippines last 2013 is an earthquake that destroyed
a lot of churches. One of them is the fall of the Tower Bell of Cebu church that was recorded on video. 
However, there's a mystery caught inside the video. 

you will see a human figure outside the church after the Tower Bell was destroyed. Long, brown hair, has beard, and wears
white clothes
